{"tid":1592231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［831］車長：831真係死左人","createTime":"2019-09-24T13:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T17:43:27.000Z","uid":228349,"like":8,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"81f495b5476de6db508e8343df9754d828111d48","tid":1592231,"uid":228349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:35:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">921係元朗收工 元朗又咁岩放催淚彈冇車返屋企﹐之後有一位好心人義載，傾計後發現原來佢係車長,佢亦都俾咗職員證我睇，但係急得制冇影到。<br />\n我問咗佢<br />\n👱🏻&zwj;♂️：831到底有冇死人?<br />\n👨🏻：之前傳車長收咗錢封口<br />\n我就去搵Supervisor求證<br />\n我哋個supervisor平時好偏激<br />\n但我問佢竟然粒聲都唔出,我覺得事有蹊蹺<br />\n就去同其他車長一齊傾<br />\n有日搵到機會去咗睇CCTV<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">確認咗真係死咗人</span>(佢有講人數 好似係六個 我個人太亂唔記得咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n之後我已經趕住落車走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能大家唔信但係我都想比大家知道多啲資訊<br />\nsorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前大整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1544367/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1544367/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n最後兩句<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">血債血償</span><br />\n<br />\n#代轉發 </span>"},{"pid":"7f2cca69c3f1a2b509fda63993503a7268013f75","tid":1592231,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"a20c95d2ec0be101ff548ab749936a1b90692445","tid":1592231,"uid":128569,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:36:49.000Z","msg":"講就係<img src=\"/assets